{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"970874c4b7","title":"一个建议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"720baba56a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"970874c4b7"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5ce23973d3","name":"佟树强"},{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"efa47c3696","type":"title","text":"一个建议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"b2b60dd96d","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院佟树强","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"ce571b54ca","type":"subtitle","text":"（佟树强：中央民族学院历史系民族学研究班学生,“蜜蜂社”成员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"52af5ee508","type":"paragraph","text":"自“一群人”提出了“取消党委制”，实行民主治校的意见后，在全校同学中展开了热烈讨论，政治系某些同志在讨论中用谩骂词句来代替说服，用画毒蛇来讽刺，这样作法，完全越出处理人民内部矛盾的范围。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"976801968a","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，对于这一问题既然存在着两种针锋相对的意见，为了分清是非，辨别真理，我建议党、团、学生会、工会、及有关方面的领导，开辟一个“专门园地”，通过大字报、壁报、辩论会……等等方式来进行讨论，以便去伪存真，达到团结，更好地管理学校的目的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"72a6f8c5ee","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要的是“百家争鸣”，而不是“两家相骂”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"482d5dd13c","type":"paragraph","text":" 群众来稿","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"},{"id":"bebbd6aadd","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7"}],"page":{"id":"a62d14b816","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"970874c4b7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}